<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="alongside-adv">alongside <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əˌlɒŋ'saɪd/    美 /əˌlɔːŋ'saɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在旁边；沿着边；并排地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He waited several minutes for a taxi to pull up alongside. 
他等了几分钟，直到一辆出租车靠边停下。</p></div></div>